parameters:
Mage Relm: It seems like even with my weight, I can go
through here!

Court Official Emoni: Finally, we can see the top floor. I
pray that there are no traitors among your companions.
Clea: None of us will betray you.

Court Official Emoni: ...Everyone says that until they are
betrayed.

Court Official Emoni: Please be careful not to have the rug
pulled out from under you as well.

Mage Relm: I will also go and check on Sophia. There might
be another trap, so we can't be too sure.
Clea: Yes, please take care of me.
Court Official Emoni: Hmph, let's go to the top floor.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
